1
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:17,073
Yeah, we both love each other,
and it’s been a long time now.

2
00:00:18,067 --> 00:00:19,530
So, what about Whan and Phaka?

3
00:00:21,063 --> 00:00:24,138
Phaka didn’t run off with me.

4
00:00:24,208 --> 00:00:27,274
She ran away 'cause
she didn’t wanna be your second wife!

5
00:00:27,571 --> 00:00:31,661
You still haven’t figured out that
Loy doesn’t like Phaka?

6
00:00:31,897 --> 00:00:34,816
...or even Whan,
as you’ve got it in your head, Phaad?

7
00:00:34,817 --> 00:00:38,345
I didn’t think you two were this messed up.

8
00:00:41,887 --> 00:00:43,506
Great! Great!

9
00:00:43,507 --> 00:00:46,704
I’ll let everyone in on your secret.

10
00:00:48,337 --> 00:00:49,613
I’m dying to know.

11
00:00:49,939 --> 00:00:53,539
...what if Phaka finds out
she’s into freaks like you?

12
00:00:54,278 --> 00:00:56,805
- ...what her reaction will be.
- Don’t even think about it, Phad!

13
00:00:57,388 --> 00:00:58,545
Please, I’m begging you.

14
00:00:59,108 --> 00:01:01,642
Fine! I won’t tell a soul.

15
00:01:02,033 --> 00:01:04,642
Alright, make Whan marry me then!

16
00:01:04,917 --> 00:01:06,981
But Whan doesn't love you, Phaad.

17
00:01:08,796 --> 00:01:10,804
Whether she loves me or not,
what does it even matter?

18
00:01:11,505 --> 00:01:14,392
That's enough, Phaad.
What do you want from me? Spit it out.

19
00:01:15,289 --> 00:01:17,623
Well, then I’ll take your sister’s virginity.

20
00:01:17,930 --> 00:01:19,331
Just once, that's all I’m asking!

21
00:01:20,559 --> 00:01:24,531
And I promise that
I'll keep this matter to laugh about by myself.

22
00:01:27,034 --> 00:01:28,429
I won’t tell a soul.

23
00:01:29,142 --> 00:01:30,350
You son of a bitch!

24
00:01:30,966 --> 00:01:32,962
Ouch...

25
00:01:33,769 --> 00:01:34,939
Drop dead!

26
00:02:00,617 --> 00:02:02,800
Hey... I didn’t mean to!

27
00:02:08,941 --> 00:02:10,561
I... I didn't do it.

28
00:02:11,015 --> 00:02:13,486
- Hey! No... I didn't do it!
- Oh my God!

29
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,388
Loy! Oh no!

30
00:02:15,795 --> 00:02:19,949
Loy! Don’t die on me!
I’ll get you to a doctor right now!

31
00:02:28,677 --> 00:02:31,718
- I can’t hold on anymore...
- Don’t you dare give up, Loy!

32
00:02:32,162 --> 00:02:33,689
Please, stay with me.

33
00:02:34,865 --> 00:02:36,754
Kaew... it really hurts.

34
00:02:38,394 --> 00:02:42,251
No! No! Don’t you dare die on me!

35
00:02:44,666 --> 00:02:46,430
Didn’t you say you loved me?

36
00:02:46,881 --> 00:02:48,895
You promised you'd be with me forever…
didn't you?

37
00:02:49,721 --> 00:02:51,272
You promised, damn it—don’t you dare break it!

38
00:02:51,974 --> 00:02:53,675
Don’t you dare die on me!

39
00:02:58,972 --> 00:03:03,463
I love you, Kaew…
I swear it before heaven and earth.

40
00:03:06,423 --> 00:03:07,668
I love you, Kaew...

41
00:03:09,989 --> 00:03:14,590
Even if our love is wrong...

42
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:20,597
But I'm incredibly happy,
Kaew, that I love you.

43
00:03:27,748 --> 00:03:29,475
Since we both love each other...

44
00:03:30,634 --> 00:03:32,410
...this is between the two of us.

45
00:03:33,375 --> 00:03:35,189
Even if anyone sees it as wrong, who cares?

46
00:03:39,372 --> 00:03:41,713
But I'm so glad I had the chance to love you.

47
00:03:42,655 --> 00:03:44,551
I’ll always love you, Loy.

48
