Thanks, Kaew... really.

53
00:05:16,804 --> 00:05:18,051
I love you, Kaew...

54
00:06:53,504 --> 00:06:54,516
Loy.

55
00:06:57,400 --> 00:07:00,579
You will be in my heart forever.

56
00:07:23,694 --> 00:07:25,583
No... Loy...

57
00:07:30,770 --> 00:07:32,981
Loy! No!

58
00:07:49,699 --> 00:07:52,805
If we truly loved each other,
I wouldn’t allow things to be this way.

59
00:07:53,778 --> 00:07:57,660
But this is impossible.
You and I can never be together.

60
00:07:59,359 --> 00:08:01,473
No one will let us be together.

61
00:08:10,988 --> 00:08:12,351
Still don't get it?

62
00:08:29,071 --> 00:08:31,019
May the sacred beings be my witness.

63
00:08:32,004 --> 00:08:40,404
This Loy swears to love
and remain loyal to Kaew forever..

64
00:08:41,443 --> 00:08:47,153
This Kaew also swears to love
and remain unwaveringly loyal to Loy.

65
00:08:51,442 --> 00:08:53,633
- When love exists,
- Let it be true.

66
00:08:54,281 --> 00:08:55,284
Nothing but love.

67
00:08:56,682 --> 00:09:00,198
That’s why
I believe in this love—it will never change.

68
00:09:01,214 --> 00:09:04,167
No matter what rules anyone sets,

69
00:09:05,019 --> 00:09:07,163
They can’t define our love.

70
00:09:08,413 --> 00:09:10,365
If Loy and Kaew are forbidden to love,

71
00:09:11,865 --> 00:09:15,460
Then only death could ever tear us apart.

72
00:10:10,758 --> 00:10:22,045
It's said that fate brought us together
To meet each other like this.

73
00:10:22,786 --> 00:10:26,868
I want to keep you close to me.

74
00:10:26,869 --> 00:10:34,456
For us to stand side by side,
our hearts filled with joy.

75
00:10:34,834 --> 00:10:40,294
