76
00:10:40,723 --> 00:10:46,371
know that I'm vulnerable.

77
00:10:46,784 --> 00:10:50,846
But our love might be wrong.

78
00:10:50,847 --> 00:10:58,110
Fate might be too cruel to me.

79
00:10:58,707 --> 00:11:04,628
If we have to face the gaze
of a thousand judging eyes.

80
00:11:04,704 --> 00:11:10,678
